<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/2.9.3/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        .container-custom {
            max-width: 100px;
            /* Set the max-width to a smaller value */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="background-color: rgb(237, 246, 248);">
    <%- include('include/navbarhead') %>
        <br><br><br><br><br><br>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 style="color:rgb(96, 96, 249)">Placement Highlights</h1>
        </div>
        <br>

        <div class="container">
            <div id="accordion" role="tablist">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header mb-3" role="tab" id="headingOne"
                        style="background-color: rgb(236, 235, 235);">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true"
                                aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                About Us
                            </a>
                        </h5>
                    </div>

                    <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                        data-parent="#accordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="text-justify">The Placement & Training department plays a vital role and is
                                becoming a
                                key
                                department of
                                the Institute. From the very beginning the institute lays greater emphasis on Industrial
                                Training and Practical Training for engineering students. Employment of the students of
                                the
                                college is our major concern. The Placement Cell serves to merely bridge the gap between
                                a
                                job-aspirant and a prospective employer.</p>
                            <p class="text-justify">Placement Cell interacts with more than 200 reputed organizations
                                for
                                arranging campus interviews
                                for the final year BE students. We make efforts to organize technical seminars,
                                workshops and corporate expectation sessions. Industry personnel are invited
                                periodically to
                                enrich the knowledge of our student community with the latest technological innovations
                                and
                                industry practices. We produce graduates who are well equipped to handle the working
                                norms
                                of
                                the industry.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header mb-3" role="tab" id="headingTwo"
                        style="background-color: rgb(236, 235, 235);">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false"
                                aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                Placement Policy
                            </a>
                        </h5>
                    </div>

                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                        data-parent="#accordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3>Placement Policy</h3>
                            <ul class="list-group">
                                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Mass:</strong> Companies which recruit students with
                                    generic
                                    skill sets using a generic hiring process.</li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Core:</strong> Companies which recruit for branch
                                    and
                                    skill-specific roles.</li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Dream:</strong> Product based companies or which
                                    come
                                    under
                                    top 500 Fortune Companies or companies which offer salary more than 8 LPA.</li>
                                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Open Dream:</strong> Companies which offer salary
                                    more
                                    than
                                    20 LPA.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <br>
                            <h3>Ladder Policy: (One Job Policy)</h3>
                            <ul class="list-group">
                                <li class="list-group-item">Student placed in mass is eligible for Core, Dream and Open
                                    Dream.</li>
                                <li class="list-group-item">Student placed in core is eligible for Dream and open dream
                                </li>
                                <li class="list-group-item">Student placed in dream is eligible for open dream.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header mb-3" role="tab" id="headingThree"
                        style="background-color: rgb(236, 235, 235);">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false"
                                aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                Highest package offered during the 2021-22 is 43.18 LPA
                            </a>
                        </h5>
                    </div>

                    <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                        data-parent="#accordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <p class="text-justify"> Since the academic year 2021-22 we had the privilege of being
                                visited
                                by 450+ companies
                                including 260+ IT companies and 150+ core companies each year. A total of 3126 students
                                have
                                been placed through campus recruitment in the last five years. We had the good fortune
                                of
                                being visited by core companies specific to each domain such as Applied Materials,
                                SABRE,
                                ABB LTD., Mercedes Benz and LARSEN & TOUBRO LTD for Mechanical and Industrial &
                                Production,
                                BROADCOM & NATIONAL INSTRUMENTS for Electrical & Electronics and Electronics &
                                Communication, TCS, WIPRO for Computer Science and also by many dream companies to name
                                a
                                few, such as CISCO, VMWARE, INTUIT, IBM, AMAZON, TWILIO, GOOGLE, SAP LABS and MICROSOFT.
                            </p>

                            <p class="text-justify">Every year the placement cell plans the training activities related
                                to
                                placement and overall
                                personality development.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-5">
            <h1 style="color:rgb(96, 96, 249)">Placement Statistics</h1>
            <div class="container mt-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                                <div class="carousel-inner">
                                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="../images/stats1.jpeg" alt="First slide">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="carousel-item">
                                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="../images/stats2.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="carousel-item">
                                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="../images/stats3.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button"
                                    data-slide="prev">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                                </a>
                                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button"
                                    data-slide="next">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <br>
        <br>

        <%- include('include/footer') %>

</body>

</html>